  <brief_title>Validity of Electronic Diary for Monitoring Varicose Veins Symptoms</brief_title>
  <official_title>Performance of Daily Electronic Diary to Capture Venous Symptoms Before and After Intervention for Great Saphenous Vein Incompetence</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>BTG International Inc.</agency>
